rows.label: qst201510_0010
rows.name: Hey, won't you rely on me more?

rows.label: qst201510_0020
rows.name:
Do you know where the
Thanatitan was delivered?

rows.label: qst201510_0030
rows.name:
How sad... I guess you don't
acknowledge my power very much...

rows.label: qst201510_0040
rows.name: No, that's not it, but...

rows.label: qst201510_0050
rows.name: Just kidding...

rows.label: qst201510_0060
rows.name:
For my beloved Driver,
I'll lend a hand...

rows.label: qst201510_0070
rows.name: I see, with Azami's Clairvoyant Eye...

rows.label: qst201510_0080
rows.name: Wait a moment...

rows.label: qst201510_0090
rows.name: Well? Did you see anything?

rows.label: qst201510_0100
rows.name:
In a place like a giant ether
mine, men were working.

rows.label: qst201510_0110
rows.name:
A large device I've never seen
before was installed there...

rows.label: qst201510_0120
rows.name:
And next to it was the Thanatitan.
I also saw a Gulan man nearby...

rows.label: qst201510_0130
rows.name: ...An ether mine?

rows.label: qst201510_0140
rows.name: Is there such a place in Invidia, mo?

rows.label: qst201510_0150
rows.name: It's in Superbia...

rows.label: qst201510_0160
rows.name: You can see that far?

rows.label: qst201510_0170
rows.name: Yes...

rows.label: qst201510_0180
rows.name: So no matter how far apart we are...

rows.label: qst201510_0190
rows.name:
...I am always watching
my beloved Driver.

rows.label: qst201510_0200
rows.name: Creepy...

rows.label: qst201510_0210
rows.name:
S-So, it's an ether mine
in Superbia, right?

rows.label: qst201510_0220
rows.name: That's right.

rows.label: qst201510_0230
rows.name: What could that large device be?

rows.label: qst201510_0240
rows.name: It must be something like Sakura, mo.

rows.label: qst201510_0250
rows.name:
But then, there would be no need
for the Thanatitan, would there?

rows.label: qst201510_0260
rows.name:
If they're using Thanatitan at a
place where ether is being mined...

rows.label: qst201510_0270
rows.name:
Then the mysterious device is for
carrying the Thanatitan, mo?

rows.label: qst201510_0280
rows.name:
The flow of ether is like the flow of blood.
Following it leads into the Divine Beast's body...

rows.label: qst201510_0290
rows.name:
If Thanatitan is used there, the decline of
Superbia's Divine Beast will accelerate...

rows.label: qst201510_0300
rows.name: Then we have to hurry.

rows.label: qst201510_0310
rows.name:
If the culprit succeeds, Superbia
will be in grave danger.

rows.label: qst201510_0320
rows.name:
Indeed. We must return to Superbia
at once and capture the culprit.

rows.label: qst201510_0330
rows.name: This is getting exciting...
